    public final class IdeStateListener
extends IdeListener
implements LaunchListener, PerspectiveListener
    A listener of IdeStateChange events. This listener creates IdeStateChangeDto data transfer objects and passes them to the Activity Watcher Service to be transferred into the User Activity Client Application for further processing.
